#!/bin/sh
# deliberate-mcp has merged into the unified `think-and-ship` server as of v0.2.0.
cat <<'MSG' >&2
deliberate-mcp has merged into the `think-and-ship` server.

  Install:        npm i -g think-and-ship
                  cargo install think-and-ship

  MCP config:     command = `think-and-ship`, args = ["serve"]

Tool names: prefer `think_*` (canonical). The old `deliberate_*` names
remain wired as deprecated aliases through v0.2.x.

See https://github.com/AlrikOlson/think-and-ship for details.
MSG
exit 1
